    },
    "3": {
      "title": "Bolts",
      "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Bolts\">Bolts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Skyrim:Rare_Curios_Items&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Bolts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Unlike steel and Dwarven bolts, these can be forged anywhere if you have joined the <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Dawnguard_(faction)\" title=\"Skyrim:Dawnguard (faction)\">Dawnguard</a>. They can also be purchased from <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Sorine_Jurard\" title=\"Skyrim:Sorine Jurard\">Sorine Jurard</a> after the quest <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:A_New_Order\" title=\"Skyrim:A New Order\">A New Order</a>.\nAll bolts can still only be crafted by being a member of the Dawnguard faction and speaking with Sorine after A New Order.\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable sortable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th class=\"unsortable\">\n</th>\n<th>Name (<a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Form_ID\" title=\"Skyrim:Form ID\">ID</a>)\n</th>\n<th width=\"22\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_(square).png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Weight\"><img alt=\"Weight\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/22px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/33px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/44px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th width=\"22\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Value\"><img alt=\"Value\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/22px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/33px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/44px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th width=\"22\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SkyrimTAG-icon-Heavy_Attack.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Damage\"><img alt=\"Damage\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/a/ab/SkyrimTAG-icon-Heavy_Attack.png/22px-SkyrimTAG-icon-Heavy_Attack.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/a/ab/SkyrimTAG-icon-Heavy_Attack.png/33px-SkyrimTAG-icon-Heavy_Attack.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/a/ab/SkyrimTAG-icon-Heavy_Attack.png/44px-SkyrimTAG-icon-Heavy_Attack.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th>Notes\n</th>\n<th>Speed</th>\n<th>Gravity\n</th></tr>\n<tr class=\"citation\" id=\"Bonemold_Bolt\">\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-weapon-Bonemold_Bolt.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-weapon-Bonemold Bolt.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/9/91/SR-icon-weapon-Bonemold_Bolt.png/48px-SR-icon-weapon-Bonemold_Bolt.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/9/91/SR-icon-weapon-Bonemold_Bolt.png/72px-SR-icon-weapon-Bonemold_Bolt.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/9/91/SR-icon-weapon-Bonemold_Bolt.png/96px-SR-icon-weapon-Bonemold_Bolt.png 2x\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"citation\" id=\"FExxx840\">Bonemold Bolt<br /><span class=\"idall\"></span><span class=\"idall\">(<span class=\"idref\"><span class=\"idcase\">FE</span><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Form_ID#Creation_Club\" title=\"Skyrim:Form ID\"><span style=\"cursor:help;\" title=\"These three digits vary depending on installed Creations. Click for more details.\">xxx</span></a><span class=\"idcase\">840</span></span>)</span><span class=\"idall\"></span>\n</td>\n<td>0\n</td>\n<td>3\n</td>\n<td>15\n</td>\n<td>Can be forged using <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Bonemeal\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Bonemeal\">bonemeal</a> and the <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Steel_Smithing\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Steel Smithing\">Steel Smithing</a> perk.\n</td>\n<td rowspan=\"5\">5400\n</td>\n<td rowspan=\"5\">0.35\n</td></tr>\n\n\n<tr class=\"citation\" id=\"Corkbulb_Bolt\">\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-weapon-Corkbulb_Bolt.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-weapon-Corkbulb Bolt.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/50/SR-icon-weapon-Corkbulb_Bolt.png/48px-SR-icon-weapon-Corkbulb_Bolt.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/50/SR-icon-weapon-Corkbulb_Bolt.png/72px-SR-icon-weapon-Corkbulb_Bolt.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/5/50/SR-icon-weapon-Corkbulb_Bolt.png/96px-SR-icon-weapon-Corkbulb_Bolt.png 2x\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"citation\" id=\"FExxx832\">Corkbulb Bolt<br /><span class=\"idall\"></span><span class=\"idall\">(<span class=\"idref\"><span class=\"idcase\">FE</span><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Form_ID#Creation_Club\" title=\"Skyrim:Form ID\"><span style=\"cursor:help;\" title=\"These three digits vary depending on installed Creations. Click for more details.\">xxx</span></a><span class=\"idcase\">832</span></span>)</span><span class=\"idall\"></span>\n</td>\n<td>0\n</td>\n<td>6\n</td>\n<td>10\n</td>\n<td>Can be forged using <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Corkbulb_Root\" title=\"Skyrim:Corkbulb Root\">corkbulb root</a> or purchased from <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Khajiit_Traders\" title=\"Skyrim:Khajiit Traders\">Khajiit caravans</a><br />Have a 25% chance to <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Paralyze_(effect)\" title=\"Skyrim:Paralyze (effect)\">paralyze</a> the target for 4 seconds.\n</td></tr>\n\n\n<tr class=\"citation\" id=\"Iron_Bolt\">\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-weapon-Iron_Bolt.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-weapon-Iron Bolt.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/6/66/SR-icon-weapon-Iron_Bolt.png/48px-SR-icon-weapon-Iron_Bolt.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/6/66/SR-icon-weapon-Iron_Bolt.png/72px-SR-icon-weapon-Iron_Bolt.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/6/66/SR-icon-weapon-Iron_Bolt.png/96px-SR-icon-weapon-Iron_Bolt.png 2x\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"citation\" id=\"FExxx83A\">Iron Bolt<br /><span class=\"idall\"></span><span class=\"idall\">(<span class=\"idref\"><span class=\"idcase\">FE</span><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Form_ID#Creation_Club\" title=\"Skyrim:Form ID\"><span style=\"cursor:help;\" title=\"These three digits vary depending on installed Creations. Click for more details.\">xxx</span></a><span class=\"idcase\">83A</span></span>)</span><span class=\"idall\"></span>\n</td>\n<td>0\n</td>\n<td>1\n</td>\n<td>8\n</td>\n<td>Can be forged at any level, without the need of any perks.\n</td></tr>\n\n\n<tr class=\"citation\" id=\"Orcish_Bolt\">\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-weapon-Orcish_Bolt.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-weapon-Orcish Bolt.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/7/72/SR-icon-weapon-Orcish_Bolt.png/48px-SR-icon-weapon-Orcish_Bolt.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/7/72/SR-icon-weapon-Orcish_Bolt.png/72px-SR-icon-weapon-Orcish_Bolt.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/7/72/SR-icon-weapon-Orcish_Bolt.png/96px-SR-icon-weapon-Orcish_Bolt.png 2x\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"citation\" id=\"FExxx841\">Orcish Bolt<br /><span class=\"idall\"></span><span class=\"idall\">(<span class=\"idref\"><span class=\"idcase\">FE</span><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Form_ID#Creation_Club\" title=\"Skyrim:Form ID\"><span style=\"cursor:help;\" title=\"These three digits vary depending on installed Creations. Click for more details.\">xxx</span></a><span class=\"idcase\">841</span></span>)</span><span class=\"idall\"></span>\n</td>\n<td>0\n</td>\n<td>3\n</td>\n<td>12\n</td>\n<td>Can be forged using the <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Orcish_Smithing\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Orcish Smithing\">Orcish Smithing</a> perk.\n</td></tr>\n\n\n<tr class=\"citation\" id=\"Silver_Bolt\">\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-weapon-Silver_Bolt.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-weapon-Silver Bolt.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/4/43/SR-icon-weapon-Silver_Bolt.png/48px-SR-icon-weapon-Silver_Bolt.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/4/43/SR-icon-weapon-Silver_Bolt.png/72px-SR-icon-weapon-Silver_Bolt.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/4/43/SR-icon-weapon-Silver_Bolt.png/96px-SR-icon-weapon-Silver_Bolt.png 2x\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"citation\" id=\"FExxx83F\">Silver Bolt<br /><span class=\"idall\"></span><span class=\"idall\">(<span class=\"idref\"><span class=\"idcase\">FE</span><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Form_ID#Creation_Club\" title=\"Skyrim:Form ID\"><span style=\"cursor:help;\" title=\"These three digits vary depending on installed Creations. Click for more details.\">xxx</span></a><span class=\"idcase\">83F</span></span>)</span><span class=\"idall\"></span>\n</td>\n<td>0\n</td>\n<td>2\n</td>\n<td>10\n</td>\n<td>Can be forged at any level, without the need of any perks.\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by content3.uesp.net\nCached time: 20260720152104\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.029 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.058 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1176/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 0/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 14318/8388608 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 2689/8388608 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/1000\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   24.759      1 -total\n 53.58%   13.265      5 Template:Item_Data\n 28.39%    7.028      1 Template:Weight_Icon\n 25.87%    6.405      5 Template:IDs2\n 21.73%    5.380      3 Template:Icon_Base\n 16.24%    4.021      5 Template:ID\n  9.01%    2.231      1 Template:Value_Icon\n  8.43%    2.088     10 Template:Highlightable_Entry\n  8.10%    2.005      1 Template:Damage_Icon\n-->\n</div>"
