    "4": {
      "title": "Food",
      "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Food\">Food</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Skyrim:Rare_Curios_Items&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Food\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Both of these items are created by <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Cooking\" title=\"Skyrim:Cooking\">cooking</a> them in a pot. Chokeberries can be purchased from Babette.\nPlacing a poisoned apple in an NPC's inventory and waiting results in the NPC's death. Waiting time varies and occasionally poison fumes become visible. This does not require the <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Poisoned\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Poisoned\">Poisoned</a> Pickpocketing perk.\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable sortable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th class=\"unsortable\">\n</th>\n<th>Name (<a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Form_ID\" title=\"Skyrim:Form ID\">ID</a>)\n</th>\n<th width=\"22\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_(square).png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Weight\"><img alt=\"Weight\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/22px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/33px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/44px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th width=\"22\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Value\"><img alt=\"Value\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/22px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/33px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/44px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th>Effect(s)\n</th>\n<th class=\"unsortable\">Ingredients\n</th>\n<th class=\"unsortable\">Notes\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-food-Poisoned_Green_Apple.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-food-Poisoned Green Apple.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2c/SR-icon-food-Poisoned_Green_Apple.png/48px-SR-icon-food-Poisoned_Green_Apple.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2c/SR-icon-food-Poisoned_Green_Apple.png/72px-SR-icon-food-Poisoned_Green_Apple.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2c/SR-icon-food-Poisoned_Green_Apple.png/96px-SR-icon-food-Poisoned_Green_Apple.png 2x\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td><span id=\"Poisoned_Green_Apple\"></span>Poisoned Green Apple<br /><span class=\"idall\">(<span class=\"idref\"><span class=\"idcase\">FE</span><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Form_ID#Creation_Club\" title=\"Skyrim:Form ID\"><span style=\"cursor:help;\" title=\"These three digits vary depending on installed Creations. Click for more details.\">xxx</span></a><span class=\"idcase\">849</span></span>)</span>\n</td>\n<td>0.1\n</td>\n<td>3\n</td>\n<td>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Lingering_Damage_Health\" title=\"Skyrim:Lingering Damage Health\">Apple Poisoning</a>, 4 pts for 60 secs</li></ul>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Chokeberry\" title=\"Skyrim:Chokeberry\">Chokeberry</a><br /><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Green_Apple\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Green Apple\">Green Apple</a>\n</td>\n<td>\n<ul><li>Silently harm enemies by placing poisoned apples in their pockets.</li></ul>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-food-Poisoned_Red_Apple.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-food-Poisoned Red Apple.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/e/e2/SR-icon-food-Poisoned_Red_Apple.png/48px-SR-icon-food-Poisoned_Red_Apple.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/e/e2/SR-icon-food-Poisoned_Red_Apple.png/72px-SR-icon-food-Poisoned_Red_Apple.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/e/e2/SR-icon-food-Poisoned_Red_Apple.png/96px-SR-icon-food-Poisoned_Red_Apple.png 2x\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td><span id=\"Poisoned_Red_Apple\"></span>Poisoned Red Apple<br /><span class=\"idall\">(<span class=\"idref\"><span class=\"idcase\">FE</span><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Form_ID#Creation_Club\" title=\"Skyrim:Form ID\"><span style=\"cursor:help;\" title=\"These three digits vary depending on installed Creations. Click for more details.\">xxx</span></a><span class=\"idcase\">D98</span></span>)</span>\n</td>\n<td>0.1\n</td>\n<td>3\n</td>\n<td>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Lingering_Damage_Health\" title=\"Skyrim:Lingering Damage Health\">Apple Poisoning</a>, 4 pts for 60 secs</li></ul>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Chokeberry\" title=\"Skyrim:Chokeberry\">Chokeberry</a><br /><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Red_Apple\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Red Apple\">Red Apple</a>\n</td>\n<td>\n<ul><li>Silently harm enemies by placing poisoned apples in their pockets.</li></ul>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by content2.uesp.net\nCached time: 20260720152105\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.011 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.029 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 324/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 0/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 1790/8388608 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 317/8388608 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 5/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/1000\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 76/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   12.447      1 -total\n 47.42%    5.902      1 Template:Weight_Icon\n 34.65%    4.313      2 Template:Icon_Base\n 20.36%    2.534      2 Template:ID\n 17.58%    2.189      2 Template:Anchor\n 13.62%    1.695      1 Template:Value_Icon\n-->\n</div>"
